---
import GitHubIcon from "@/components/GitHubIcon.astro";
import LinkedInIcon from "@/components/LinkedInIcon.astro";
---

<section class="relative isolate flex overflow-hidden bg-neutral">
  <div
    aria-hidden="true"
    class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 z-[-1] scale-110 bg-linear-to-br from-primary/15 via-neutral via-50% to-secondary/15 opacity-80 blur-3xl"
  ></div>
  <div class="mx-auto">
    <h1 class="text-7xl font-space-grotesk font-bold">
      Construyendo el <span class="text-primary">Futuro</span>, una linea a la vez.
    </h1>
    <p class="font-inter text-xl text-gray-400">
      Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur, adipisicing elit. Id nam qui
      quisquam et eius doloribus, atque, eos soluta repudiandae corporis
      quibusdam saepe sunt vitae iure laboriosam amet suscipit doloremque
      facere.
    </p>
    <div class="flex my-5 space-x-4 [&>a]:inline-block">
      <a href="https://github.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
        <GitHubIcon
          classStyles="h-8 w-8 transition hover:scale-130 hover:text-primary duration-300"
        />
      </a>
      <a href="https://linkedin.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
        <LinkedInIcon
          classStyles="h-8 w-8 transition hover:scale-130 hover:text-primary duration-300"
        />
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <aside class="hidden md:block">
    <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Provident, sint. In neque animi reprehenderit deleniti magni iste expedita consequatur cumque labore, officia doloremque sint voluptates nemo id possimus dolores quibusdam.</p>
  </aside>
